column5: Anyone have e-mail addrtess or phone number or address of bait shops in Fort francis or DrydenThanksJimbo

jimbo - you can do a search for "canadian yellow pages" on google.com or mamma.com then go to the yellow pages site and enter bait shops or fishing shops for those towns. i got a number ofshops when i did this but don't have them here with me now.phish
